Algorithm 2. GraphSAGE minibatch forward propagation algorithm

Input : Graph G(V, E);
input features {x_v, ∀v ∈ B};
depth K; weight matrices W^k, ∀k ∈ {1, ..., K};
non-linearity σ;
differentiable aggregator functions AGGREGATE_k, ∀k ∈ {1, ..., K}
neighborhood sampling functions, N_k : v → 2^V, ∀k ∈ {1, ..., K}

Output: Vector representations z_v for all v ∈ B

1 B^K ← B;
2 for k = K...1 do
3 | B^{k-1} ← B^k ;
4 | for u ∈ B^k do
5 || B^{k-1} ← B^{k-1} ∪ N_k(u);
6 | end
7 end
8 h^0_u ← x_v, ∀v ∈ B^0 ;
9 for k = 1...K do
10 | for u ∈ B^k do
11 || h_N(u) ← AGGREGATE_k({h^{k-1}_{u'}, ∀u' ∈ N_k(u)});
12 || h^k_u ← σ(W^k · CONCAT(h^{k-1}_u, h_N(u)));
13 || h^k_u ← h^k_u / ||h^k_u||_2;
14 | end
15 end
16 z_u ← h^K_u, ∀u ∈ B

